com.solacesystems.solclientj.core.handle

Interface StatsSupport

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FlowHandle, SessionHandle

    public interface StatsSupport
    The StatsSupport interface provides a common API for retrieving and clearing API statistics. Applications do not need to instantiate or extend objects with this interface. This interface is already included in all the solclientj interfaces where it is required:
    • SessionHandle
    • FlowHandle

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Clears statistics
